title: 2NE1 Global Tour (Japanese Edition)
description:
This is the Japanese version of 2NE1'S "Global Tour: New Evolution", just got it two days ago so I'm uploading it for everyone to enjoy! I know it can be hard to get your hands on the DVD..

Tracklisting:
Track Listing   [Disc-1] 01 I'm the best I 02 Fire 03 Clap your hands 04 I Do not Care (Reggae Mix) 05 Do not Stop The Music 06 Don't Cry & You And I - Bom 07 Try to follow me 08 Please Do not Go - CL & Minzy 09 Pretty Boy 10 Kiss - Dara 11 Hurts 12 Lonely 13 In The Club 14 Stay Together 15 I Love You 16 Ugly 17 Let's Go Party 18 Hate You 19 Go Away 20 Can't Nobody 21 I Don't Care 22 I'm better than I (Encore) [Disc-2] 01 Making Film 02 Multi Angle - Go Away

Screenshots will be uploaded later:)
Enjoy everyone!!
P.S: Obviously if you know anything about 2NE1 the songs are in Korean with the exception of scream!
